Package: commitgenius
Version: 0.2.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Hasanul Banna <bannawandoor27@gmail.com>
Description: AI-powered CLI tool for generating conventional commit messages
 Commitgenius is a command-line tool that uses local LLMs via Ollama
 to generate conventional commit messages from git diffs.
 .
 Features:
  * Generates smart, conventional commit messages
  * Works with local LLMs through Ollama
  * Supports multiple Ollama models
  * Fast and efficient
  * Works offline with local models
Homepage: https://github.com/bannawandoor27/Commitgenius
Depends: ollama
